G. DAVENPORT / San Antonio Express-News; Photo, The boardinghouse in Los 
Angeles where DeHoyos lived for a time. ; Photo, Santa Ana Police Chief Paul 
Walters, left, Capt. James Dittman and Sgt. John McClain at news conference. 
KEN HIVELY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
