TRAFFICKING -- LATIN AMERICA; DRUG TRAFFICKING -- UNITED STATES; FOREIGN DEBT; 
LATIN AMERICA -- FINANCES; CENTRAL AMERICAN PEACE; USSR -- FOREIGN POLICY -- 
