A Wells Fargo Bank branch in Buena Park was robbed Monday when a man who had 
waited in a bank line pulled a handgun out of a leather attache case and gave a 
note to the teller that said: "I'm holding you up. Don't push any buttons, and 
give me all the big bills too." 
