'88 CAR THEFTS SPURT IN COUNTY, REPORT SHOWS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By GEORGE BUNDY SMITH, Times Staff Writer 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
