Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
LOS ANGELES DODGERS (BASEBALL TEAM); CINCINNATI REDS (BASEBALL TEAM); GIBSON, 
KIRK; ROSE, PETE; FANS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
