Organization, the West Hills Community Organization and the Valley Industry and 
Commerce Assn. are sponsoring a public forum for the 3rd District candidates 
Wednesday at 7:30 p.m., at El Camino Real High School, 5440 Valley Circle 
Blvd., Woodland Hills. 
